room_title: Escape room "The Cartel Mansion" by Lost Key Escape Rooms in Williston
room_description: The Edenburg Diamond, the rarest and most expensive diamond valued at 1 Billion Dollars has been stolen by the Mexican Cartel run by the Jefe Pablo Chaconne. You and your team (The Wilistona Cartel) want it and will do anything to get it. Your task is to break into the mansion and steal the diamond before the Cartel returns home. Can you bypass his security and make it out alive?
